    public class DataSetViewer
extends CentredDialog
implements SOMToolboxApp
    Implements a JDialog for displaying a 2 or 3 dimensional data set. It is basically a wrapper around Plot2DPanel and Plot3DPanel, respectively.
    The data given has to follow the same format as expected by the Plot2DPanel and Plot3DPanel , i.e. an double[][], where the first index is the data item, and the second index are the X, Y and possible Z coordinates, i.e. an array of double[#items][2] or double[#items][3].
